<event name="LOSTSUN_FLEET_UNLOCK1" unique="true">
	<preventQuest/>
	<text>A Lost Sun vessel is nearby, their captain frantically pacing back and forth. "You there- you side with the Federation? You must assist us. It is of the highest importance."</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Listen to their request.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Our leader, Admiral Ariadne's personal cruiser has been taken by Inquisition forces at these co-ordinates. You must rescue her under any conditions, or else we are doomed. The Federation is the Lost Suns' only ally, we must rely solely on your efforts for our continued survival."</text>
			<quest event="LOSTSUN_FLEET_UNLOCK2"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>We don't have the time.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The Rockman merely grunts and flies away.</text>
			<choice>
				<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
				<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
			<choice>
				<text>Do nothing.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="LOSTSUN_FLEET_UNLOCK2">
	<preventQuest/>
	<preventFleet/>
	<quest>
		<nebulaBeacon>false</nebulaBeacon>
		<aggressive>2</aggressive>
	</quest>
	<beaconType id="map_icon_lostsun" global="true">
		<color r="255" g="94" b="94" a="1.0"/>
	</beaconType>
	<text>The fleet the Lost Suns mentioned isn't present at the co-ordinates they gave, but the cruiser is! The ship hails you, a gruff Rockman with a scar down his eye staring you down. "The Inquisition has recovered this vessel, and the same shall be for this entire sector. It would be wise for the Federation to cut ties with the Lost Suns and leave at once, or face the wrath of a second Inquisition. It is only a matter of time until the Theocracy rises again; which side do you want to be on?"</text>
	<ship load="SHIP_LOSTSUN_UNLOCK" hostile="false"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>You're right, the Lost Suns are a pathetic ally to the Theocracy's strength.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"So you have changed your mind so suddenly? What makes you say these words?"</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>The Lost Suns are rash and violent. The Theocracy knows how to time its strikes.</text>
				<event>
					<text>The Rockman on the camera changes his composure. "You know nothing then. Too easily persuaded, an unworthy ally to the Lost Suns. Be glad you get off easy, I would much rather squish your head had I orders not to."</text>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>The Inquisition has failed before.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"THE INQUISITION HAS NEVER FAILED! We have merely... paused our efforts, until the time is right. The Coalition shall be the spark that reignites the fires of fury in our hearts."</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Spoken like a true Lost Sun.</text>
				<event>
					<text>"You dare insult the might and grace of the Elder's holy crusades? You die here!"</text>
					<ship hostile="true"/>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Continue...</text>
						<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>This isn't a hill to die on. Leave.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Remain silent and leave.</text>
		<event/>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="LOSTSUN_FLEET_UNLOCK3">
	<text>"Yes, and it is safe to say you have passed. The Lost Suns are not sparing with their alliances. If you truly represent the Federation, then you have done a good job showing your loyalty. The Theocracy will resent ever having crossed our path with you on our side."</text>
	<variable name="ach_boss_lostsun" op="set" val="1"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event>
			<text>"It would be criminal to not extend aid to you as well. I will provide you with quality military supplies to assist you. I have already begun the transfer of the blueprints for this very ship to the Federation, in hopes it will be used in their fight."</text>
			<variable name="ach_crew_ariadne" op="set" val="1"/>
			<unlockCustomShip silent="false">PLAYER_SHIP_LOSTSUN</unlockCustomShip>
			<crewMember amount="1" class="unique_ariadne" combat="2">Ariadne</crewMember>
			<autoReward level="HIGH">standard</autoReward>
			<weapon name="RANDOM"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_boss_rockcruiser">
		<text>As a matter of fact, I did overthrow the Rock government once.</text>
		<event>
			<text>Ariadne breaks into laughter, but stops. "My stars, you ARE the ship we heard about. Overthrow is hardly the word, but you have sent their homeworlds into chaos! Your efforts have been a considerable aid to ours. Allow me to help you in every way I can."</text>
			<variable name="ach_crew_ariadne" op="set" val="1"/>
			<unlockCustomShip silent="false">PLAYER_SHIP_LOSTSUN</unlockCustomShip>
			<crewMember amount="1" class="unique_ariadne" combat="2">Ariadne</crewMember>
			<autoReward level="HIGH">standard</autoReward>
			<upgrade amount="2" system="weapons"/>
			<reveal_map/>
			<damage amount="-30"/>
			<weapon name="RANDOM"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

